  "2026-07-11T16:06:23.750Z",maintainer-agent,"Faucet evidence 2026-07-11 (PR#512 lane): 7/7 closes leaked structured resolution fields (je50/d30l/zuw8/9ugc/qd2h/ypha/pmmv had close_reason only; resolution/expected/actual absent) — first leak after two consecutive zero-leak lanes (PR#506 0/9, PR#511 0/4). Trend 278->285, backfilled same day by maintainer-agent -> back to 278. Lane authors codex-root + maintainer-agent used pm close -m without pm update structured fields. Confirms close-time completeness gate (this item) is still the missing control: zero-leak lanes were author discipline, not tooling."
